As for example usage of native library, we have
```C++
SkRRect rrect;
SkVector radii[4] = {{40, 40}, {40, 40}, {40, 40}, {40, 40}};
rrect.setRectRadii(rect, radii);
```
It helps draw rounded rectangle with custom radii for each corners.
